data.description: NEW ROOF (09/2023) on this Stunning 4/2/2 Block/Stucco, Fenced Home in the highly sought after neighborhood of Orange Blossom Hills in Summerfield. Location is Perfect with this home tucked away on a dead end road but only minutes to get to The Villages, shopping centers, restaurants, medical offices, CR 42, 441/27 and 301. This freshly painted split bedroom floor plan features 1642 square feet, vaulted ceilings, new ceiling fans with light fixtures, new vinyl plank flooring in the living/dining, hallway and master closet and tile in all other areas plus an inside laundry room. The kitchen has tons of cabinet and counter space, newer stainless steel appliances with a brand new stove and a large double door pantry for your extra storage needs. The 2 car garage floor was just epoxied, the garage door, door opener and keypad are all new (9/23.) There is also a new bladder in the well. Another bonus, for your peace of mind, there is an ADT alarm system and cameras installed outside. Please call today for your private showing, don’t let this opportunity pass you by!
